# Pem API (`api/`)

**Package:** NestJS app under **`api/`** — `npm install`, `npm run start:dev`, `npm run build` from `api/`. No shared runtime code with `mobile-app/`. **Internal imports:** use **`@/`** → **`src/`** (see **`pem-coding-standards.mdc`**, `api/tsconfig.json`); Nest emits relative requires in **`dist/`**.

**Stack:** **NestJS** ~11, **Drizzle ORM** + **`pg`**, **pgvector** (vector similarity search), **Clerk** JWT (**`jose`** + JWKS), **Svix** for `POST /webhooks/clerk`, **`@nestjs/throttler`**, **`ValidationPipe`**. **Config** — **`src/core/config/configuration.ts`** (loaded from **`AppModule`**). **OpenAI** via **Vercel AI SDK v6** (`generateText` + `Output`, `embed`, never `generateObject`). **Link previews** — **`OgHtmlReaderService`** in **`MediaModule`** (`src/modules/media/links/`): SSRF-guarded **`fetch`** + **Cheerio** parse of **`og:title`**, **`og:description`**, **`og:image`** (plus `<title>` fallback); metadata is stored on **`message_links`** (`page_title`, `structured_summary`, `extracted_metadata` for image URL). **`jina_snapshot`** remains a nullable legacy column. **BullMQ** — **`BullModule.forRootAsync`** + **`ScheduleModule.forRoot()`** in **`AppModule`**; **`ChatModule`** and **`MediaModule`** each call **`BullModule.registerQueue({ name: 'chat' })`** so **`InjectQueue('chat')`** resolves in the controller and in **`ChatVoiceUploadService`**; **`BriefsModule`** registers **`weekly-planning`**; processors live in **`MessagingModule`** / **`BriefsModule`**. **Expo** push — **`notifyInboxUpdated`**. OpenAI **Whisper API** for voice transcription.

**Tables (Drizzle: `src/database/schemas/`):** **`users`** (incl. **`timezone`** IANA, **`notification_time`** for morning brief), **`messages`** (**`role`**: `user` | `pem`, **`kind`**: `text` | `voice` | `brief`, content, voice_url, transcript, **`triage_category`**, **`processing_status`**, polished_text, parent_message_id), **`message_links`** (URLs in a user message: original + normalized URL, canonical URL, page title, content type, optional legacy **`jina_snapshot`** jsonb, structured summary / OG description, **`extracted_metadata`** jsonb e.g. `image_url`, fetch_status, fetched_at; FK `message_id` → messages; **24h user-scoped cache** on `normalized_fetch_url`), **`message_embeddings`** (pgvector 1536-dim, FK to messages), **`extracts`** (tone, **urgency** `'someday'|'none'` — all timing via `period_start`/`period_end`/`due_at`, **`meta`** jsonb for rarely-queried fields, batch_key, status; **`message_id`** FK to messages; calendar event fields), **`calendar_connections`**, **`reported_issues`**, **`logs`** (unified audit: types include `chat`), **`memory_facts`**.

**Chat pipeline (workflow-style agent):** User sends message → `POST /chat/messages` → save → enqueue BullMQ `chat` job → return immediately (no triage/agent on the HTTP path; with **R2**, recorded-voice **Whisper** also runs in the worker after `downloadObject`; without R2, Whisper runs in **`ChatVoiceUploadService`** because there is no blob to fetch).

**Recall / triage invariants:** **Triage + moderation** run on **user-facing text** (caption and/or transcript for image or voice+photo turns), not the full vision-injected agent blob. **URLs for link fetch** come from the same user-facing surface (not vision OCR) unless product explicitly expands that later. **Photo recall** (thumbnail strip + `similaritySearchImageMessages`) targets **user rows with stored vision** — `kind: 'image'` **or** `kind: 'voice'` with non-empty `image_keys` + `vision_summary`, not “image kind only.” **`message_embeddings`** rows use deterministic **head+tail truncation** before embed, with **one retry** on failure (length-only logs). **`ChatProcessor.mergeRapidMessages`** **skips merging** when any primary/peer message is **`kind: 'image'`** or has **`image_keys`**, so peer photo rows are never collapsed into a single text-only pipeline run.

`ChatOrchestratorService` processes:
1. **Transcribe** (deferred voice with R2: Whisper in worker + `message_updated`; otherwise transcript already on the row)
2. **Link reading** (when the message contains URLs): **URL-only messages** run OG HTML fetch before triage; **mixed messages** fetch only for `question_only` | `needs_agent`. **`ChatLinkPipelineService`** stores **`message_links`** and injects **OG title + description (+ image when present)** into Ask + Pem agent prompts so **`memory_writes`** can carry substance. **`GET /chat/messages`** attaches **`link_previews`** for display.
3. **Triage** (`TriageService`, gpt-4o-mini, routing-only) → `trivial` | `question_only` | `off_topic` | `needs_agent`
4. **Route:**
   - `trivial` → quick acknowledgment
   - `off_topic` → short redirect (weather, trivia, general knowledge — Pem does not engage)
   - `question_only` → `ChatQuestionService` (RAG + extracts + memory + gpt-4o; only *their* data)
   - `needs_agent` → **`PemAgentService`** — **prompt chaining** (Anthropic-style workflow): (1) **extraction** pass → `creates` / `updates` / `completions` only, low temperature, retries + JSON recovery; (2) **orchestration** pass → `response_text`, calendar, memory, scheduling, etc., using locked extraction JSON in the prompt; if orchestration fails, **synthesized** reply from extraction counts; if extraction stays empty but heuristics say the message is actionable, **monolithic** single-call fallback (full schema, same retries + recovery as before)
   - **Context to the agent:** open tasks (inbox/snoozed), upcoming timed items from those tasks, **today’s** timed subset, **done** extracts (last 90 days), **dismissed** extracts (last 30 days, to avoid re-extracting), last **30** chat messages (chronological), memory facts (prompt section **capped** in `ProfileService`), scheduling slots/prefs, **RAG** (same `buildAgentRagSearchParams` + enrichment as Ask when recall planner fires), **temporal “Messages from {period}”** block when `detectQuestionTemporalRange` hits, **saved links recall** (`buildSavedLinksRecallPromptSection`), **photo recall** prompt block when the intent path attaches. **Programmatic dedupe:** new `creates` that match an open or recently dismissed task (normalized, case-insensitive) are dropped before DB apply.
5. **Apply** agent output: creates, updates, completions, calendar_writes, memory_writes
6. **Respond** — save Pem response message, publish via SSE, push notification
7. **Embed** chat lines into pgvector (background): **user** messages after successful handling; **Pem** replies when saved. **Idempotent** per `message_id` (unique index). Stored text is `[ISO] user:|pem: …` for RAG clarity.

**SSE:** `GET /chat/stream` — `X-Accel-Buffering: no`, **heartbeat** every **30s** (type `heartbeat`), events: `status`, `pem_message`, `message_updated`, `processing_failed` (final job failure). Redis pub/sub via `ChatEventsService` (`chat-events:{userId}`).

**Chat idempotency & jobs:** `POST /chat/messages` optional **`idempotency_key`** (unique per user) returns the existing message if replayed. BullMQ job id **`chat-msg:{messageId}`** dedupes duplicate enqueue. Worker **attempts: 3**, exponential backoff; logs **messageId** only (no user text). Pipeline skips work if `processing_status` is already **`done`**.

**Morning brief:** `BriefCronService` — hourly cron checks user timezones, generates brief at midnight (user local), saves as `kind: 'brief'` Pem message, delayed push at user's `notification_time`.

**Calendar integration:** Google Calendar only (server-side OAuth + API via `googleapis`). Agent can emit `calendar_writes` to create events. OAuth `state` is **HMAC-signed** with env **`GOOGLE_OAUTH_STATE_SECRET`** (required whenever `GET /calendar/google/auth-url` is used); callback verifies signature + expiry before `upsertGoogle`.

**AI models:** `gpt-4o-mini` for triage. `gpt-4o` for PemAgent, question answering, morning brief. `text-embedding-3-small` for pgvector embeddings. `whisper-1` for voice.

**API:**

```
POST /chat/messages     ← send message: JSON body (`kind` text, voice, or image), or `multipart/form-data` with file field `audio` for recorded voice (optional `image_keys`, `idempotency_key` form fields or `?idempotency_key=` for voice)
POST /chat/photos/upload-url ← presigned PUT to R2 for `chat-images/{userId}/{uuid}.ext`; client PUTs then POSTs message with `kind: image`
GET  /chat/messages     ← paginated history (?before=ISO&limit=50); image rows include signed `image_urls` when R2 is configured
GET  /chat/stream       ← SSE (one per user session)

GET  /extracts/done|open|query|:id|:id/history
PATCH /extracts/:id/done|dismiss|undone|undismiss|snooze|reschedule
PATCH /extracts/:id — user edit (partial JSON: text, urgency `someday|none`, batch_key, due_at, period_start, period_end, period_label, duration_minutes, pem_note, is_deadline, energy_level, tone; calendar-linked tasks reject schedule fields)
POST /extracts/:id/report

PATCH /users/me/timezone
GET  /calendar/connections
GET  /calendar/google/auth-url
GET  /calendar/google/callback
PATCH /calendar/connections/:id/primary
DELETE /calendar/connections/:id
```

**Layout:**

| Area | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/core/` | Cross-cutting infra: **`config/`**, **`bootstrap/`** (`configureApp`), **`auth/`** (Clerk JWT guard, decorators, JWKS helpers), **`utils/`** (logging, sleep, dedupe helpers, **URL stack**: SSRF guard, tracking-param strip, normalize for fetch, link regexes, extract occurrences, ISO-week, Amazon image URL upgrade, markdown title hint). |
| `src/database/` | Drizzle **`schemas/`**, **`database.module.ts`**, constants — unchanged as the persistence layer. |
| `src/modules/` | **`chat/`** — thin HTTP surface: **`chat.controller.ts`**, **`chat.module.ts`** (composes submodules + **`chat`** queue), **`dto/`**, **`constants/chat.constants.ts`**, **`helpers/chat-inbound.helpers.ts`**. **`messages/`** — **`ChatService`** (message CRUD / serialization). **`memory/`** — **`EmbeddingsService`**. **`media/`** — voice (Whisper upload path), photo (vision, recall, dedup), links (OG HTML **`OgHtmlReaderService`**, **`ChatLinkPipelineService`**), signed URLs. **`agent/`** — **`PemAgentService`**, **`PemAgentLlmService`**, **`OrchestratorLlmService`**, **`question/`** (Ask path). **`messaging/`** — SSE (**`ChatStreamService`**), **`ChatEventsService`**, triage, **`ChatOrchestratorService`**, scheduler, client list hydration, **`jobs/chat.processor`**. **`briefs/`** — morning brief + weekly reflection crons/LLM/processor. **`users/`**, **`calendar/`**, **`extracts/`**, **`lists/`**, **`push/`**, **`profile/`**, **`storage/`**, **`health/`**. |
| `src/app.module.ts`, `src/main.ts` | Application root. |

**Drizzle:** Change schema in TS → **`npm run db:generate`** → review → **`npm run db:migrate`**. Never hand-edit `drizzle/*.sql` or `drizzle/meta/`.

**Security:** Validate input; **`ClerkAuthGuard`** + DB user id from JWT. **CORS:** `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` must be a non-empty comma-separated list — bootstrap throws if missing (no wildcard / reflective fallback). **Prod:** **`OPENAI_API_KEY`** must be set or config load fails (fail-fast).

**Maintenance:** When **schema, routes, queues, or env** change, update **this file** in the same effort. See **`pem-project.mdc`**.
